Installation instruction for source and binary tar.gz package
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

1. Linux
~~~~~~~~
a. From source package

   Build and install:
   $ tar -xzf mm8dread-0.1.tar.gz
   $ ./configure
   $ make
   # make install

   Remove:
   # make uninstall

b. From binary package

   Install:
   # tar -xzf mm8dread-0.1-i586.tar.gz
   # cd mm8dread
   # ./create_links
            or
   # tar -xzf mm8dread-0.1-i586.tar.gz
   # cd mm8dread
   # ./install

   Remove:
   # cd mm8dread
   # ./remove_links
   # cd ..
   # rm -r mm8dread
            or
   # /opt/mm8dread/uninstall

2. Windows
~~~~~~~~~~
a. From source package

   Build and install:
   > tar -xzf mm8dread-0.1.tar.gz
   > build.bat
   > build.bat install

   Remove:
   > build.bat uninstall

c. From binary package

   > unzip mm8dread-0.1-win32.zip

